schedule.pizza
==============

The easiest way to find some time. Designed for agents, built for humans.

API
---

::

    GET  /api/v1/availability?user={username}
    POST /api/v1/book
    GET  /api/v1

Development
-----------

::

    pnpm install
    pnpm dev
    pnpm build
    pnpm deploy

